channel.title: OblivionScape Anti-leech Help
channel.description:
At first i thought i was doing something wrong but i soon realized that sanity the owner made some sort of anti leech. when you try to connect to the server your client displays a message saying "no response from server please try using a different world" so if anyone has figured this out or wants to try to help, id apreciate it.
i have portforwarded and it didnt help.. i have used other servers they work just fine.. this is the first time this has ever happened.
